```aria
vec3:position = vec3(100.0, 200.0, 300.0);

// Memory layout (16 bytes with padding):
// [float x = 100.0] [float y = 200.0] [float z = 300.0] [padding = ???]
//  ↑ 4 bytes         ↑ 4 bytes         ↑ 4 bytes         ↑ 4 bytes
```

